OWASP ZAP (Zed Attack Proxy)

OWASP ZAP is a web security testing tool used to find vulnerabilities in web applications.

Features:
Intercepts HTTP requests
Automated vulnerability scanning
Detects SQL Injection, XSS
Free and open-source
Example:

While testing a website, ZAP detects a Cross-Site Scripting (XSS) vulnerability in a search input field.
